# Local AI / contributor context index

**Do not delete this file.** It is the navigation map for humans and agents; extend it when behavior or layout changes.

**Tracked in git** (not ignored) so clones keep the map. Edit anchors if line numbers drift.

---

## Quick navigation

| Area | Primary files |
|------|----------------|
| HTTP API + persistence (`data/chores.json` or optional SQLite) | `server.js`, `lib/login-throttle.cjs`, `lib/sqlite-store.cjs` |
| HTML shell + ids | `index.html` |
| Events, auth, mutations | `js/main.js` |
| i18n (`t`, locales, language in Settings) | `js/i18n.js`, `locales/en.json`, `locales/de.json` |
| Dashboard + log + scheduled DOM | `js/render.js` |
| Presets, points, quick bar | `js/presets.js` |
| Shared state | `js/state.js` |
| Styles (split by feature) | `css/chore-tracker-*.css` |
| Docker (prod image, compose, GitHub clone / auto-pull) | `Dockerfile`, `docker-compose.yml`, `Dockerfile.gitclone`, `Dockerfile.autopull`, `docker-compose.autopull.yml`, `docker/entrypoint-sync.sh`, `.github/workflows/docker-image.yml` |
| Automated tests (Node built-in runner, CI) | `test/*.test.cjs`, `npm test`, `.github/workflows/ci.yml` |

